snippet.title: nerdSlayer Studios
snippet.description:
Hello everyone I am N.S. (nerdSlayer) and I provide critical analysis & opinions on video games. Think of me as a detective trying to get to the bottom of things. I specifically focus on investigating dead/dying games or companies , and help people understand why said game or company failed. Most of the analysis comes from analysis of other perspectives/reviews, my interpretation of credible sources, and finally is ultimately from my own opinions & experiences. Videos edited by Tom Davies.

If you use ad-block but like my content, feel free to donate to my Patreon. This will help support me as I do this fulltime. You can pledge as little $1. Goals are outlined there.

Channel rules listed on our Discord! https://imgur.com/a/EhjtHVY

If you are interested in possible business/sponsorship opportunities, whether content, appearance, or commentary based please email me with more details. If you are interested in hiring me as a consultant, feel free to contact me concerning my rates.
